<h3 id="doc-custom-color">Custom Color</h3>
<p>You can customize button colors using utility classes by combining
<code>.btn</code> with background color utilities like
<code>.bg-[color]-[shade]</code> and
<code>.hover:bg-[color]-[shade]</code>.</p>
<button class="btn bg-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-400 mt-4 text-black">
Light Blue Button
</button>
<pre class="html"><code>&lt;button class=&quot;btn bg-blue-300 hover:bg-blue-400&quot;&gt;Simple Button&lt;/button&gt;</code></pre>
